      <text>A transmission by facsimile is not considered an electronic transfer for the purposes of this chapter.</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>B.</num>
      <text>A carrier shall accept the electronic transfer of the uniform consultation referral form.</text>
    </para>
  </section>
